      <listPerson>
        <person xml:id="p_14">
          <persName type="preferred">Nṛsiṃharāya II</persName>
          <persName type="variant">Nṛsiṃhāmātya</persName>
          <trait type="son" key="p_15">
            <label>Ānandarāyamakhin</label>
          </trait>
          <floruit from="1735" to="1736">ca. 1735-36</floruit>
          <note>Grandson of Nṛsiṃharāya I, who was the brother of Tryambakarāyamakhin and Bhagavantarāyamakhin. He was minister of Ekoji II alias Bāvā Saheb (Raghavan, Intro to Śāhendravilāsa, p. 28)</note>
          <note>Since he was the minister of Ekoji II, who ruled around 1735-36, I take the latter as his date of activity.</note>
        </person>
